{"title":"哨所春歌","authors":["姚成友"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨所春歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士　姚成友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霸道的北风呼呼刮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连夜的冷雨哗哗下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云雾山中海防哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑语滔滔把春光描画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方腊梅迎飞雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方椰树顶云霞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨长摊开世界地图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展现一幅春光明媚的图画："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"委内瑞拉山林的烽火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象枝枝绽开的春花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圣多明各的枪声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象春雷漫空劈炸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果河中的春潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托战船向殖民主义者进发；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越竹林里的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映透了漫天的朝霞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，钢枪、战斗、胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，东风、红旗、骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士心中的春歌呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能把万丈冰融化！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨中掠过战士的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡逻小路洒下朵朵马蹄花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草丛中亮着战士的刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双目炯炯注视风云变化！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}